<section class="defra-section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="about-heading">About this library</h2>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    This library exists so that prompts worth keeping do not stay trapped in one team.
    When a Defra developer writes a prompt that genuinely improves the quality of their work,
    it belongs here — shared, documented, and available to every team.
  </p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    The bar for inclusion is high. A prompt makes it into the library because it has been
    tested on real work and produces consistently good results. Browse, use, and contribute.
  </p>
</section>
